########### Process management ###############

create_new_process
	fork.c  : Create a process using fork
	vfork.c : Create a process using vfork

daemon_process
	daemon.c : Create a process a daemon and run it in background
  	
	Procedure to validate the daemon process
	*) Run daemon.c (./daemon)
	*) It will create a file ('daemon.txt') and write it 
	   'Daemon process....' as it in the background process
	*) To validate the ouput
		'cat daemon.txt' 

	*)To stop the daemon process
		ps -ef | grep daemon
		kill -9 <pid_of_daemon>
	

